<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>They have been presenting their Heart Breakfast radio show throughout the pandemic. </p>

<p>And Amanda Holden and her co-presenter Ashley Roberts shared a fun video to Instagram on Tuesday after another day on air.</p>

<p>The Britain's Got Talent judge, 49, and Pussycat Dolls star, 38, commanded attention as they strutted down the hallway at Global studios while flicking their hair. </p>

